# HCS review checklist (pointer)

When reviewing a PR in this repo, check:

- [ ] Single ring touched (or explicit justification in PR description for multi-ring)
- [ ] No cross-ring imports
- [ ] Policy lives in canonical location (system-config), not in this repo
- [ ] No universal shell execution tool added
- [ ] No audit-write agent endpoint added
- [ ] `OperationShape` upstream of `CommandShape`
- [ ] Evidence includes provenance (source, observed_at, authority, parser_version, confidence)
- [ ] Dashboard impact considered
- [ ] Schema changes: Zod + JSON Schema + ontology.md + tests moved together
- [ ] Policy changes: `hcs-policy-reviewer` objections filed
- [ ] Schema changes: `hcs-ontology-reviewer` objections filed
- [ ] Security-sensitive: `hcs-security-reviewer` objections filed
- [ ] ADR status current (proposed / accepted / superseded)
- [ ] Charter version cited in PR description
- [ ] `just verify` green

Authority: `docs/host-capability-substrate/implementation-charter.md` v1.1.0+
